<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-deDibujosAUnAlgoritmo" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Sample response: Kiran wrote the numbers he was subtracting as a sum of hundreds, tens, and ones. Then he saw he needed more ones, so he decomposed a 10 into more ones. </li>
      <li>Sample response: Kiran crossed out the 90 and wrote 80 above it. Then he crossed out the 1 and wrote 11 above that because he had 10 more ones after he decomposed a 10. </li>
      <li><m>100 + 70 + 6</m></li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


